      "widgets_values": [
        "# Save Metadata Patch To GenAsset\n\n1. Paste `token` from GenAsset Settings -> Tokens.\n2. Paste `version_id` from the asset page using **Copy version id**.\n3. Edit `metadata_patch_json` with your keys.\n4. Queue this single node.\n\nExpected result:\n- Node UI text starts with `SUCCESS:`.\n- `status_json` output has `ok: true`.\n- The same version in GenAsset shows merged metadata.\n\nIf it fails:\n- Check `status_json.error`.\n- Make sure token + version belong to the same workspace.\n- Ensure `metadata_patch_json` is valid JSON."
